description:
Redline 3 takes you through the snowy mountains of the Himalayans.
Avalanches,blind turns,jumps and stalactites block your path on this racing inspired level.
borrows heavily from Fast Racing Neo alpine thrust

Big thanks to phimeek for the alpine tree
